milestones.description: Max Walker has become the top wicket-taker for AUS in ODIs with 17 wickets, going past Gary Gilmour's 16
Doug Walters has broken the record for most catches (6) in ODIs for AUS, going past Greg Chappell's 5
Constant has broken the record for officiating the most ODIs (9) as an umpire, going past Dickie Bird
Tony Greig has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (20) for ENG, going past Fletcher
Greg Chappell has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (14) for AUS, going past Ian Chappell
Tony Greig has broken the record for most catches (7) in ODIs, going past Holder's 6
Tony Greig has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (20), going past Fletcher
